sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Player as Browser Player
  participant Client as @phalanxduel/client
  participant Server as Fastify WS/App
  participant Shared as @phalanxduel/shared
  participant Engine as @phalanxduel/engine

  Player->>Client: Choose move in match UI
  Client->>Server: WS action + telemetry envelope
  Server->>Shared: Parse and validate action schema
  Server->>Engine: applyAction(current GameState, Action)
  Engine-->>Server: PhalanxTurnResult + PhalanxEvent[]
  Server->>Shared: Compute hashes and serialize view model
  Server-->>Client: Broadcast gameState + turn result
  Client-->>Player: Render updated battlefield, phase, and log cues
